{"id":306878,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-各地维权者要求释放被拘留的内蒙访民赵/","date":"2013-08-01T18:32:37Z","modified":"2013-08-01T18:32:37Z","title":"维权网 | 各地维权者要求释放被拘留的内蒙访民赵玉兰和刘亚珍（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span>内蒙赵玉兰、刘亚珍因多年诉求无果而欲到中南海告状，当即被府右街派出所送马家楼，由内蒙古驻京办接回后，当地对赵玉兰、刘亚珍行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span>赵玉兰、刘亚珍的四个儿女到中南海要妈妈，被府右街派出所送久敬庄，因孩子太小又被久敬庄赶了出来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵玉兰、刘亚珍因举报内蒙古赤峰市宁城县水利局副局长高殿军，内蒙古赤峰市宁城县水利局执法队队长法蔚云，以权谋私，多年纵容沙场老板王力成、王国明、王刚非法踩沙，为其牟取暴利而撑打保护伞，为其披上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>合法踩砂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的外衣，掩盖毁灭耕地到事实危害。因非法踩砂遗留的深坑造成了多起重大事故，致</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>人死亡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为了反腐、为了悲剧不再发生，赵玉兰、刘亚珍进京告御状，被内蒙古赤峰市宁城县公安局行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>天。维权访民得知此消息后对赵玉兰、刘亚珍表示支持、声援，并呼吁立即释放赵玉兰、刘亚珍。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加声援活动的有：吉林赵云侠、刘凤杰、张继新，黑龙江初东芳、于丽华、王玉波、张国志，山东林秀丽等人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--dY4EGdlBwg/UfqAcovJyGI/AAAAAAAAmOg/XreL78vARHQ/s1600/PHTO0006.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"203\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--dY4EGdlBwg/UfqAcovJyGI/AAAAAAAAmOg/XreL78vARHQ/s320/PHTO0006.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZYPscPfrnhU/UfqAc6A_GSI/AAAAAAAAmOk/IrKCKvsm3Gk/s1600/PHTO0011.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"196\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZYPscPfrnhU/UfqAc6A_GSI/AAAAAAAAmOk/IrKCKvsm3Gk/s320/PHTO0011.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}